[{"id":"RAW_ebdbcf7f","title":"全网最详细的 Codex 入门教程，手把手教你玩转 Vibe Coding。","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679828&idx=1&sn=6e1c0a935c70c566ee765c02a36327a6","date":"2026-02-09 01:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ebdbcf7f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"数字生命卡兹克","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":24,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_4ead9a68","title":"Yelp 如何构建 “Yelp Assistant”","link":"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/how-yelp-built-yelp-assistant","date":"2026-02-09 16:31:03","oneSentenceSummary":"本文详细介绍了 Yelp 如何将其 AI 助手从 RAG 原型转变为高性能、生产级系统的工程案例研究。","summary":"文章探讨了 Yelp Assistant 的架构演进，重点关注从基础的检索增强生成（RAG）原型到稳健生产环境的转变。它详细介绍了四个关键的数据策略转变：通过混合流式/批处理流水线确保数据新鲜度；将结构化事实与非结构化评论分离；利用文本和嵌入实现混合图片检索；以及通过统一的内容获取 API 实现集中访问。此外，它还描述了将单体 LLM 解构为用于护栏和关键词生成的专用模型；通过并行化和分层模型优化推理效率，将延迟从 10 秒降低到 3 秒以下；以及建立使用 LLM-as-a-judge 的多维度评估框架。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4ead9a68.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"ByteByteGo Newsletter","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_401505dd","title":"3 年、1 万人，快手技术团队首次系统披露 AI 研发范式升级历程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651274822&idx=1&sn=b4b364a2e23df2beda37e877001ea4df","date":"2026-02-09 05:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_401505dd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":59,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_48ab1cdc","title":"2026 年硅谷书单：18 位硅谷创始人共同推荐的 56 本书","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMDMxOTI2NA==&mid=2649104479&idx=1&sn=358e90989ecf328bc6bc47d22be5e315","date":"2026-02-09 09:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_48ab1cdc.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"十字路口Crossing","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_ed39a1a3","title":"快手用“对齐”技术，让广告推荐更懂你","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODk