itle":"借助 AI Coding 快速打造 AI Agent 系统","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558316&idx=1&sn=6a53c77fe9bdb8b35a1d513897c4a472","date":"2026-02-09 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bdde6ae5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":37,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_5585a96a","title":"即梦 Seedance2.0 视频模型\"王者归来\"之后 | 最新突发: 模型太强以至禁止了真人人脸支持...","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247489943&idx=1&sn=b77584f14c2c449d78b6c1e169cc67b1","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5585a96a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Web3天空之城","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_96a3c531","title":"2026-02-09 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-09-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-09 08:57:18","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_96a3c531.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":67,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_d27d64c0","title":"2026 年人工智能+的共识与分歧","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&mid=2650995868&idx=1&sn=13d05fefc47f3f8d7c390ee54154aa58","date":"2026-02-09 08:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d27d64c0.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯研究院","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_65540b0c","title":"Agent 热潮年度回望：一切火爆早有预兆","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691564643&idx=1&sn=944679ca719b61ae9ee8f5623926b84e","date":"2026-02-09 06:27:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_65540b0c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯科技","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":28,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_31a5ecbe","title":"独家对话极映科技高鑫：我们为什么要做一个比 Sora 难 10 倍的物理世界模型？｜甲子光年","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5OTI0NTc3Mg==&mid=2247550046&idx=1&sn=d1dde2b15410f494c3f07ad9bf549ff6","date":"2026-02-09 05:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_31a5ecbe.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"甲子光年","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":33,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_34f828c","title":"智能体可观测性赋能智能体评估","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=reISMhbZ2XE","date":"2026-02-09 20:44:02","oneSentenceSummary":"本次网络研讨会探讨了可观测性如何作为评估非确定性 AI 智能体的核心基础，将关注点从调试代码转向调试推理过程。","summary":"Harrison Chase (LangChain CEO) 和 Vivec (Deep Agents 负责人) 讨论了从确定性软件到非确定性 AI 智能体的根本转变。他们认为，由于智能体逻辑是在运行时产生的，传统的代码调试已不足够，这使得可观测性追踪 (Traces) 成为了新的“事实来源”。会议定义了可观测性的分层框架——Runs、Traces 和 Threads，并解释了这些元素如何支持离线、在线和即时评估。实践见解包括利用生产环境追踪构建测试集、实施中间件钩子以防止“异常”智能体行为，以及利用自动化分析对复杂编程任务中的失败模式进行分类。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_34f828c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"LangChain","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":23,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_eec4183","title":"150: 年末 AI 回顾：从模型到应用、从技术到商战，拽住洪流中的意义之线","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/698a6ac11ff460059c061b9b","date":"2026-02-09 23:15:00","oneSentenceSummary":"全方位深度复盘 2025 年 AI 全球产业图谱，涵盖底层模型技术演进、Agent 应用落地、大厂组织商战及具身智能趋势。","summary":"本期播客是《晚点聊》针对 2025 年 AI 领域的深度年终回顾。内容系统性地分为七大章节：首先探讨了 Agentic Model 的崛起，以 DeepSeek R1 为代表的推理模型通过开源和低成本路径颠覆了行业认知；其次分析了应用层面的爆发，指出 2025 年是 Agent 元年，Coding 能力已成为 Agent 执行复杂任务的核心手段；在商业竞争维度，剖析了字节跳动、阿里、腾讯在 AI 人才引进与组织架构调整上的战略差异；随后对具身智能和 AI 硬件（如 AI 眼镜）的供应链优势、数据获取瓶颈及落地场景进行了客观评估。最后，节目回归到“人”的视角，探讨了 AI 带来的薪酬溢价、就业替代以及人类在自动化洪流中对生存意义的重构。整体分析兼具技术深度与商业洞察，为技术从业者提供了一份清晰的 AI 演进地图。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_eec4183.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"晚点聊 LateTalk","resourceType":"PODCAST","readTime":6,"score":93}]
